metadata.name: NOT A TICKET
metadata.description:
**This is not a ticket to the Sail Nouns event**  
**PROP 173**  
**Sail Nouns in the New York Harbor for NFT.NYC 2023**  
  
**Date:**  
April 15th

**Schedule:**  
14:00 - Meet at Manhattan Yacht Club  
14:00-15:00 Board yachts (The last boat leaves at 14:40)  
15:00-16:00 Manhattan Skyline  
16:00-17:00 Manhattan Bridge  
17:00-18:00 Statue of Liberty  
18:00-19:00 Return to Manhattan Yacht Club

**Address:**  
140 Dudley St  
Jersey City, NJ 07302

**Instructions**  
If you own a noun then you just need to come to Manhattan Yacht Club on the date of the event.  
If you know someone who might be of a great value to the NounsDAO then you can invite that person. Please keep in mind that the event capacity is 150 guests.  
1. **Option 1.**  
Join a 110 feet sail yacht Arabella (great choice if you like comfort and want be on a big boat with other 120 guests)

2. **Option 2.**  
Join a J/24 sailboat (great choice if you want to learn how to sail and are not afraid of cold water. There will be 7 boats available 5 guests per boat)

If you have any questions, please feel free to reach out to fiveoceans_dev on Twitter, The Jungle, or Nounish discord servers.
